  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MAListener
    Creates an EventListener object specific to a Module, only used by ModuleManagement after Module loading
    Module
    The Module is an extension of the Shell entirely.
    ModuleEvent
    Event used to communicate with modules without being within the same scope of the modules.
    ModuleManagement
    Resource class which manages all Modules, and is launched by Launch in its initialization functions.
